snippet.title: Divine Duel - Official Season 2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for Divine Duel to see what to expect with Season 2 of the VR fighting game, which brings a free battle pass and the new playable hero Flint, the Astroravager. Divine Duel is available on Quest App Lab and Pico, and Season 2 is available now.

#Gaming #VR #GameTrailers
